# Supabase

## Single project
- Schema: `supabase/schema.sql`. Seed + demo user: `supabase/seed.sql`.
- Client reads/writes with **anon** key + RLS as today.

## Tables (Phase 1)
- `profiles` (id = auth user id)
- `wedding_budgets` (unique `user_id`, upsert on save)

## Client env
- `VITE_SUPABASE_URL`, `VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY` in Vercel **client** project and `client/.env.local`.

## Redirect URLs
- Must list every client origin + `/auth/callback` (local `http://localhost:5173`, production client host).

## When changing schema
- Update `schema.sql`, `seed.sql`, and `client/src/shared/lib/types.ts` together.
